'''Melbourne Gass''' is a former [[Canada|Canadian]] politician who served for 9 years as the [[Member of Parliament]] for [[Malpeque (electoral district)|Malpeque]].  He served for two years as the leader of the [[Prince Edward Island Progressive Conservative Party]] before leaving public life.

